109
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,540
I don't know.

110
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,340
She...

111
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,580
After she got out of

112
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,380
the mental hospital that year,

113
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:56,660
