114
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,520
and hit someone.

115
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:02,500
Did you visit her when you adopted me
into the Xia family?

116
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,020
I didn't.

117
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:06,300
But every year, I sent people

118
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:07,240
to the mental hospital

119
00:05:07,700 --> 00:05:08,920
