122
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,160
No.

123
00:05:15,820 --> 00:05:18,920
Miaomiao,
are you feeling alright?

124
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:21,120
It's nothing.

125
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,560
I paid my respect to her

126
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,900
